snippet.textDisplay:
It won't be the tint. If u had a patch test and didn't react to that then it will be the perm solution.

I work in a salon that has a hairdressing and beauty section and we had a client come in for a lash perm and tint. She wasn't allergic to the tint but definitely was to the perm solution.

We apply a patch test 24hrs before and if they react to it, we won't do it.
